## Installation Commands

### Double-Click Installation (Recommended):
```bash
# Navigate to installer
cd /Users/imorgado/SPLICE/dist

# Double-click SPLICE-Installer-6.0.8.pkg
# Follow on-screen prompts
```

### Command-Line Installation:
```bash
# Install for all users (requires sudo)
sudo installer -pkg dist/SPLICE-Installer-6.0.8.pkg -target /

# View installation log
tail -f /tmp/splice-installer.log
```

### Verification:
